3:1 COMMENT "# `os.args` returns the program's arg vector (position 0 is argv[0])."
3:70 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# `os.get_env` returns `option.some value` on hit, `option.none` on"
4:68 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# miss. `os.exit` terminates immediately with the given status."
5:64 EOL "\n"
